MODULE: src/security
FILES: index.js, guard.js, permission-guard.js, system-guard.js, confirmation-manager.js, param-sanitizer.js
RESPONSIBILITY: Security layer - permission checks, command sanitization, confirmation flows, system protection

INTERFACES:
- PermissionGuard: check user permissions by role (admin, user)
- SystemGuard: block dangerous commands (rm -rf, sudo, etc.)
- ConfirmationManager: require user confirmation for risky ops
- ParamSanitizer: sanitize command parameters against injection
- guard.js: unified guard orchestrator

DEPENDENCIES:
- imports: src/config: permission and security settings

UPDATED: 2026-03-16
